description:
During a routine network sweep, Vault Security detected an unauthorized transmission originating from inside the Commonwealth University campus grid. The message was flagged by the intrusion detection system before it could leave the perimeter, but the contents are obfuscated. Command suspects a cadet has been leaking vault access credentials to an outside party. The timestamp puts the transmission at 02:34 AM — well outside authorized access hours.

Intercepted Packet Payload: wbvmu qbttxpse jt tfdsfudpef

Decrypt the message and report the plaintext to the Vault Security Officer to determine what was being leaked — and to who. Submit your answer in the format: flag{your answer here}
